      <p style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; color: #555555; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Define capabilities as plan entitlements and attach them to your subscription tiers. Bachs automatically grants and revokes them as customers subscribe, upgrade, or churn.</p>
      <p style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #333333; line-height: 1.65; border-left: 2px solid #e5e5e5; padding-left: 1rem;">No more manual flag management. Your product just knows what each customer has access to — in real time, via a single API call.</p>
